    "body" : "<pre class=\"lang-java prettyprint-override\"><code>String hash = HashUtil.hash(hanaDok.getFileName());\n\nQuery query = entityManager.createQuery(&quot;SELECT o FROM OracleDok o WHERE o.fileNameHash = :hash&quot;, OracleDok.class);\n\nquery.setParameter(&quot;hash&quot;, hash);\n</code></pre>\n<p>This avoids encryption issues and is efficient for lookups.</p>\n"
